description: The majority of voters view Immigration and Customs Enforcement with suspicion, according to a new poll.  A YouGov survey released over the weekend found that 53% of respondents somewhat or strongly disapprove of ICE, compared to 39% who approve of the way they are operating. Over half of respondents said ICE’s tactics are too forceful, compared […]
